pageContext.claim: “They'll make Washington DC a state and many other places, guaranteeing two, four or six additional left wing senators....You'll have lots of, you'll have another 30 or 40 congressional people from places you've never even heard of.”
pageContext.analysis: There is certainly support for District of Columbia statehood among Democrats and also Puerto Rico. That would be four new senators. But we have no idea why Trump suggests there could be six additional senators, including from places people in Georgia have never heard of. (Guam? The Northern Mariana Islands?)
